  "Recommended:": "推薦:",
  "Apply": "套用",
  "The instruction sent to the model. Defines how the tracker generates data.": "發送給模型的指令。定義追蹤器如何生成資料。",
  "The JSON schema defining the output structure. Must be valid JSON.": "定義輸出結構的JSON模式。必須是有效JSON。",
  "Removes all tracker snapshots from this chat. Settings preserved.": "刪除所有追蹤器快照。設定保留。",
  "Resets injection method, profiles, lorebook mode, etc. to defaults. Tracker data preserved.": "重設注入方法等為預設值。追蹤器資料保留。",
  "ScenePulse internal debug log (normalizer, extraction, generation).": "ScenePulse內部偵錯日誌（正規化、提取、生成）。",
  "Full browser console output including SillyTavern and other extensions.": "包含SillyTavern和擴充的完整控制台輸出。",
  "Raw tracker JSON from the most recent generation.": "最近生成的原始追蹤器JSON。",
  "In Separate mode, this is the full API response. In Together mode, this is the extracted JSON block that was stripped from the AI's narrative response.": "分離模式為完整API回應。合併模式為提取的JSON。",
  "The AI writes its normal response, then appends tracker JSON at the end. ScenePulse automatically extracts and hides the JSON.": "AI撰寫回應後附加追蹤器JSON。ScenePulse自動提取並隱藏。",
  "If the AI omits the tracker payload, ScenePulse can automatically run a separate API call to recover. Requires a connection profile to be configured.": "如AI遺漏資料，ScenePulse可自動單獨API呼叫恢復。需設定連線。",
  "Dramatic": "戲劇性",
  "Intense": "激烈",
  "Comedic": "喜劇",
  "Twist": "轉折",
  "Exploratory": "探索性",
  "None suggested yet": "暫無建議",
  "After the AI responds, a separate quiet API call generates the tracker JSON independently. Expect ~250–300s total per message (narrative + wait + tracker).": "AI回應後，靜默API獨立生成追蹤器JSON。每則訊息~250–300秒。",
  "✓ Single API call — typically ~100–120s total": "✓ 單次API — ~100–120秒",
  "✓ No profile switching — eliminates message deletion risk": "✓ 無需切換設定 — 無刪除風險",
  "✓ AI has full narrative context for accurate tracking": "✓ AI擁有完整上下文",
  "✓ 2–3× faster than Separate mode in practice": "✓ 比分離模式快2–3倍",
  "✗ Uses tokens from the main response budget (~1,700 tokens for tracker)": "✗ 使用主回應代幣（~1,700）",
  "✗ May slightly reduce narrative length on token-limited models": "✗ 可能略微減少敘述長度",
  "✓ Clean responses — narrative never token-competes with tracker": "✓ 乾淨回應 — 不爭奪代幣",
  "✓ Dedicated token budget for tracker output": "✓ 追蹤器專用代幣預算",
  "✓ Can use a different connection profile/preset": "✓ 可以使用不同的設定/預設",
  "✗ Two API calls per message — 2–3× slower than Together mode": "✗ 每則訊息兩次API — 慢2–3倍",
  "✗ ~12s dead time between calls (chat save + preset switching)": "✗ 呼叫間~12秒空閒",
  "✗ Tracker prompt is ~10K+ tokens at 8 context msgs — reduce to 3–4 for speed": "✗ 8條訊息時~10K+ — 減少到3–4",
  "✗ Profile switching can cause message deletion (race condition with other extensions)": "✗ 設定切換可能導致訊息刪除",
  "✗ Embeds previous snapshot into narrative call (~1.9K tokens) unless Embed snapshots = 0": "✗ 嵌入快照≠0時含上一快照（~1.9K）",
  "How many recent messages to include when generating tracker updates.": "生成追蹤器更新時包含多少條最近訊息。",
  "Separate mode only — Together mode uses ST's full context automatically.": "僅限分離模式 — 合併模式自動使用ST上下文。",
  "Fastest. Good for simple 1-on-1 scenes (~5K token prompt)": "最快。適合一對一場景（~5K）",
  "Balanced. Recommended for most scenes (~8–12K tokens)": "均衡。推薦大多數場景（~8–12K）",
  "Better continuity for complex multi-character scenes (~12–20K tokens)": "複雜多角色場景連續性（~12–20K）",
  "Maximum context but significantly slower and more expensive": "最大上下文但更慢且更貴",
  "This is the biggest factor in Separate mode speed. At 8 msgs your tracker prompt is ~10K tokens — doubling roughly doubles generation time. Lower values (3–4) can cut tracker time by 40–60%.": "分離模式速度最大因素。8條訊息~10K — 翻倍時間翻倍。3–4減少40–60%。",
  "Separate mode only.": "僅限分離模式。",
  "How many times to retry if the tracker API call returns invalid JSON.": "無效JSON時重試次數。",
  "Built-in preset: temp=0.6, top_p=0.95, freq_pen=0.15, max_tokens=4096. Optimized for structured JSON output on GLM-5.": "內建預設：temp=0.6, top_p=0.95, freq_pen=0.15, max_tokens=4096。GLM-5 JSON最佳化。",
  "Embed recent scene snapshots into the narrative conversation context so the AI can reference tracker state while writing. Only applies in Separate mode. The tracker's own API call always receives the previous snapshot regardless of this setting.": "將場景快照嵌入敘述上下文。僅分離模式。追蹤器始終接收上一快照。",
  "Each embedded snapshot adds ~1.9K tokens to your narrative prompt. Set to 0 to eliminate this overhead — the tracker API call still receives previous state independently. Set to 1 for narrative continuity (AI remembers scene details). Values above 1 are rarely beneficial.": "每個快照+~1.9K。0消除開銷。1保持連續性。1以上很少有益。",
  "Injected as invisible context — AI treats it as authoritative background info. Best for continuity without polluting the conversation.": "作為不可見上下文注入。AI視為權威背景資訊。",
  "Appears as if the user said it — some models respond more attentively.": "顯示為使用者發言 — 某些模型更專注地回應。",
  "Appears as previous AI output — can reinforce the AI's own memory but may confuse some models.": "顯示為AI之前的輸出 — 增強記憶但可能混淆。",
  "Separate generation runs an isolated API call — it needs lorebook context injected since ST won't provide it automatically.": "分離生成執行獨立API — 需注入知識庫上下文。",
  "Together mode uses the normal generation — ST already injects lorebooks into context, so including them here would be redundant.": "合併模式使用正常生成 — ST已注入知識庫，此處多餘。",
